15
00:01:14,878 --> 00:01:16,442
<i>La sua anima...</i>

16
00:01:16,833 --> 00:01:18,322
<i>non e' piu' qui.</i>

17
00:01:19,404 --> 00:01:20,454
Non c'e'...

18
00:01:20,634 --> 00:01:22,334
nessun modo per curarlo.

19
00:01:30,928 --> 00:01:32,028
Mi dispiace.

20
00:01:39,672 --> 00:01:40,672
<i>Cosa?</i>

21
00:01:41,530 --> 00:01:44,439
<i>Perche' sta curando il braccio di Pito?</i>

22
00:01:45,716 --> 00:01:47,739
<i>Fai tornare Kite normale.</i>

23
